{"tid":1394858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急！請廣傳】公務員要爬山了！","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:08:22.000Z","uid":282449,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"596287e14b12f3858442b859f9d519b7cdacc98c","tid":1394858,"uid":282449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"【緊急！請廣傳🙏】公務員要爬山了！<br />\n☆守護公務員♡溫馨提示<br />\n集會時：<br />\n1. 唔好叫任何官員下台<br />\n2. 唔好提任何獨立字眼<br />\n3. 如遇搞事者，請大叫「公務員，加油！」<br />\n4. 唔好出示任何國家/地方旗幟<br />\n5. 在集會範圍內，派罷工傳單或呼叫罷工，會對公務員構成威脅，如果派，麻煩請在其他地方<br />\n6. 請諒解公務員不能收受利益，不會接受籌款/捐款<br />\n7. 呼籲多D人出席，對公務員來說，越多人便越安全<br />\n<br />\n公務員自己出錢出力，仲犧牲前途站出來。集會期間和完場後，都必須和平、理性、非暴力。兄弟姊妹們，齊撐公務員💪"},{"pid":"0a43d0f1508558f341cf1465e328bfd132282701","tid":1394858,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=QWSXAyybcV8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DQWSXAyybcV8&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIETFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=78a46820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=QWSXAyybcV8</a><br />\n<br />\n車勁啲定盾牌陣勁啲"},{"pid":"8e7323c67c5080ec4806882a8b8e50f5ca11bb8b","tid":1394858,"uid":205915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=349248&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349248%26refer%3D&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIETFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=bb9cc801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349248%26refer%3D&h=78942401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=349248&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n支持張建宗司長<br />\n修例問題不涉及政治問題 公務員表態無可厚非"},{"pid":"e0f76508822796995707e3